Translate strings on the backend using the "sn_i18n.Message.getMessage()" API

Example usage:

Pass an array of objects containing a code and message key to configure this data broker. The message key is used to look up the sys_ui_message table.

[
    {
        "code": "sn_sow_on_call",
        "message": "contact_roster"
    }
]

For any template strings, you need to create a client state object that keeps track of the template string values and pass this state variable to this data broker

{
    "formType": "300"
}


Notes:
- Make sure to keep the client state object for template string values updated BEFORE calling this translations data broker

